---
import Header from "../../components/company/CompanyHeader.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/company/CompanyFooter.astro";

const EFFECTIVE_DATE = "September 19, 2025";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Privacy Policy & Terms • Ashak Studios</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy and Terms of Service for Ashak Studios games." />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#8D46E7" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />

    <!-- Inter (serious, clean) -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

    <!-- Header/Footer da Inter kullansın diye global değişken override -->
    <style is:global>
      :root { --ff: 'Inter', ui-sans-serif, system-ui; }
    </style>

    <style>
      :root{
        --bg:#050507; --bg-2:#0C0D12;
        --panel:#0F1016; --panel-2:#131521;
        --text:#F2F2F7; --muted:#B8B9C8; --line:#232536;
        --brand:#8D46E7; --radius:16px; --shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.45)
      }
      *{box-sizing:border-box}
      html,body{
        margin:0; padding:0;
        background:radial-gradient(1200px 400px at 50% -10%, #121327 0%, transparent 60%), var(--bg);
        color:var(--text); font:16px/1.7 'Inter', ui-sans-serif, system-ui;
        scroll-behavior:smooth;
      }
      a{color:inherit}
      .container{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 16px}
      .section{padding:56px 0}
      .hero{padding:72px 0 28px;text-align:center}
      .heading-1{font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.2px;font-size:clamp(24px,3.2vw,40px);line-height:1.15;margin:0}
      .kicker{color:var(--muted);font-weight:500;font-size:14px;margin:10px 0 0}

      .card{
        background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--panel),var(--panel-2));
        border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:var(--radius);
        box-shadow:var(--shadow); padding:20px;
      }
      .h2{font-size:clamp(20px,2.2vw,28px);font-weight:700;margin:0 0 8px}
      .h3{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin:16px 0 6px}
      .meta{font-size:13px;color:#C9CAE2}
      .list{margin:8px 0 0 18px}
      .list li{margin:4px 0}
      .sep{height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,#262944,transparent);margin:24px 0}
      .toc{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-top:14px}
      .chip{font-size:13px;padding:6px 10px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid #2D3050;background:#12142A;color:#E7E7F4;font-weight:600}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="heading-1">Privacy Policy & Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="kicker">Effective Date: {EFFECTIVE_DATE}</p>
        <div class="toc">
          <a class="chip" href="#privacy">Go to Privacy Policy</a>
          <a class="chip" href="#terms">Go to Terms of Service</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PRIVACY POLICY -->
    <section id="privacy" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="h2">Privacy Policy</h2>
          <div class="meta">Applies to: “Max On The Island” and other games published by Ashak Studios.</div>

          <h3 class="h3">1) Summary</h3>
          <p>We designed our games to respect your privacy. We do not run our own backend servers for user data and we do not collect personal data from you. Your game progress and preferences are stored locally on your device. Purchases are processed by Apple using your Apple ID.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">2) Data We Do <em>Not</em> Collect</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>No names, email addresses, phone numbers, or account credentials</li>
            <li>No precise location data</li>
            <li>No analytics or usage profiles stored on our servers</li>
            <li>No device-level personal identifiers stored by us</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="h3">3) What Is Stored On Your Device</h3>
          <p>Your coin balance, hints, level progress, language preference (82 languages available), audio settings (music/SFX), and notification preference are saved locally on your device. If you delete the app, these local records are removed with it.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">4) Purchases & Subscriptions (Apple ID)</h3>
          <p>In-app purchases and subscriptions are processed by Apple using your Apple ID. We receive non-personal purchase status (e.g., whether a purchase is active) from platform services in order to unlock features on your device. We do not receive your full payment information.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">5) Third-Party Providers</h3>
          <p>We use third-party providers only to: (i) manage subscriptions and purchase validation, and (ii) deliver advertising where applicable. These providers operate under their own privacy policies and may process limited technical information required to provide their services (for example, to confirm an active subscription or to show an ad). We do not combine this information with any data of our own.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">6) Advertising</h3>
          <p>Our games may include advertising formats such as interstitial, native, banner, and optional rewarded ads. If you upgrade to <strong>PRO</strong>, interstitial, native, and banner ads are disabled during the active subscription period; optional rewarded ads remain available so you can choose to earn in-game rewards.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">7) Children’s Privacy</h3>
          <p>Our games are suitable for a wide audience. If you are under the age required by your local law to make purchases or provide consent, please use the game with a parent or guardian.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">8) Offline Use</h3>
          <p>You can open the game offline, but we <strong>do not recommend extended offline play</strong>. When offline, purchase validation and rewarded ads cannot run; coin or hint balances may appear inconsistent until connectivity is restored and the platform confirms your entitlements. To avoid confusion, play while online whenever possible.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">9) Internationalization</h3>
          <p>The game supports 82 languages. Minor translation inaccuracies may occur; we continuously improve localization quality.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">10) Changes</h3>
          <p>We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect product or legal changes. If updated, the new version will replace this one and the “Effective Date” will be revised.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">11) Contact</h3>
          <p>If you have questions about privacy, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@ashak.co">contact@ashak.co</a>.</p>

          <div class="sep"></div>

          <!-- QUICK REFERENCE (In-Game Economy) -->
          <h3 class="h3">Quick Reference: In-Game Economy (Informational)</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>Starting balance: <strong>120 Coins</strong></li>
            <li>Skip a level: <strong>60 Coins</strong></li>
            <li>Use a hint: <strong>30 Coins</strong></li>
            <li>Rewarded ad grant: <strong>+20 Coins</strong> (optional)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TERMS OF SERVICE -->
    <section id="terms" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
          <h2 class="h2">Terms of Service</h2>
          <div class="meta">Effective Date: {EFFECTIVE_DATE}</div>

          <h3 class="h3">1) About These Terms</h3>
          <p>These Terms govern your use of our mobile games, including “Max On The Island,” published by Ashak Studios (“we,” “us”). By installing or using the game, you agree to these Terms.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">2) License</h3>
          <p>We grant you a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable, revocable license to use the game for entertainment on compatible devices. You may not reverse engineer, redistribute, or exploit the game commercially.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">3) In-App Purchases & Subscriptions</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li><strong>Platform Processing:</strong> All purchases are processed by Apple via your Apple ID. Manage/cancel subscriptions in <em>Settings &gt; Apple ID &gt; Subscriptions</em> on your device.</li>
            <li><strong>PRO (Auto-Renew Monthly):</strong> Immediately grants <strong>+300 Coins</strong> and <strong>+10 Hints</strong>, and disables <em>interstitial</em>, <em>native</em>, and <em>banner</em> ads for one month. <em>Rewarded ads</em> remain available so you can optionally earn in-game rewards.</li>
            <li><strong>Remove Ads (One-Time):</strong> Records a lifetime ad-removal entitlement to your Apple ID (excludes optional rewarded ads).</li>
            <li><strong>Coin Packs:</strong> 200, 600, and 1000 Coin purchases are tied to your Apple ID.</li>
            <li><strong>Restore Purchases:</strong> If you reinstall or change devices, use the platform’s “Restore Purchases” to re-activate your entitlements.</li>
            <li><strong>Refunds:</strong> We do not handle refunds directly. Requests are subject to Apple’s policies.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="h3">4) Gameplay & Progress</h3>
          <ul class="list">
            <li>You start with <strong>120 Coins</strong>. Skipping a level costs <strong>60 Coins</strong>; using a hint costs <strong>30 Coins</strong>.</li>
            <li>Optional rewarded ads can grant <strong>+20 Coins</strong>.</li>
            <li>You can revisit any level you have previously completed from the Levels section.</li>
            <li>Settings include toggles for music, SFX, and notifications.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="h3">5) Connectivity</h3>
          <p>The game can run offline, but prolonged offline use is discouraged. Purchases, subscription checks, and rewarded ads require internet access. If you play offline, balances or entitlements may not refresh until the device reconnects.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">6) Third-Party Services</h3>
          <p>We use third-party providers to validate subscriptions and to serve advertisements. These services are necessary to deliver paid features and optional ad rewards. Their terms and privacy policies apply to their respective processing. We do not host user data on our own servers.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">7) Content & Availability</h3>
          <p>We may update, pause, or discontinue features to improve the game or to comply with platform requirements. Where feasible, we will aim to maintain a stable experience.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">8) Warranties & Liability</h3>
          <p>The game is provided “as is” and “as available.” To the extent permitted by law, we disclaim warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, and non-infringement. Our liability is limited to the maximum extent permitted by applicable law.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">9) Age & Compliance</h3>
          <p>Comply with your local laws regarding age and purchases. If you are under the applicable age of consent, use the game under supervision of a parent or guardian.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">10) Changes to These Terms</h3>
          <p>We may revise these Terms when we add features or as laws change. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>

          <h3 class="h3">11) Contact</h3>
          <p>For support or legal questions, contact: <a href="mailto:contact@ashak.co">contact@ashak.co</a></p>

          <div class="sep"></div>
          <p class="meta">For quick navigation: <a href="#privacy">Privacy Policy</a> • <a href="#terms">Terms of Service</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
